data.description:
HONEY STOP THE CAR, THIS IS IT !! This AWESOME 3-2-2 Home cheerfully greets Guests upon entry. The Living Room is highlighted with high ceilings and an open concept floorplan. The eat-in Kitchen is efficiently designed with ample storage and counter space, newish appliances, & pantry. The Spacious Master Bedroom leads to the Master Bathroom... and the Second Bedroom on the first floor could be used as a NURSERY! Backyard is quaint, but perfect for entertaining Guests! The Home is surrounded by major highways, allowing for easy access... and is just minutes from Harrington Park Soccer Fields, Joe Pool Lake, Cedar Hill State Park, Major Restaurants, and Uptown Village Mall...Bring your HGTV, DIY Ideas to splash them on this empty canvas! Here's the plan, go under Contract today, Close in 30 days, and then invite Family and Friends over for Thanksgiving Dinner! HURRY, it won’t last long!

Information deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Buyer AND Buyers Agent to verify all information.
